5、css工具

    http://enjoycss.com/start#text/0

  (1) Transforms

       <1> Transforms
           -webkit-transform: scaleX(2) scaleY(2) scaleZ(2);
           transform: scaleX(2) scaleY(2) scaleZ(2);

       <2> Translate: 单位 px、em、％；
           -webkit-transform: translateX(10px) translateY(10px) translateZ(20px);
           transform: translateX(10px) translateY(10px) translateZ(20px);

       <3> Rotate
           -webkit-transform: rotateX(50deg) rotateY(10deg) rotateZ(30deg);
           transform: rotateX(50deg) rotateY(10deg) rotateZ(30deg);

       <4> Origin
           -webkit-transform-origin: 50% 50% 0;
           transform-origin: 50% 50% 0;

  (2) Transitions:[ property|| duration (s||ms) || transition curve || start delay (s||ms)]

       -webkit-transition: background-color 200ms cubic-bezier(0.175, 0.885, 0.32, 1.275) 10ms;
       -moz-transition: background-color 200ms cubic-bezier(0.175, 0.885, 0.32, 1.275) 10ms;
       -o-transition: background-color 200ms cubic-bezier(0.175, 0.885, 0.32, 1.275) 10ms;
       transition: background-color 200ms cubic-bezier(0.175, 0.885, 0.32, 1.275) 10ms;

       ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
       property 可以为：
           color,
           font-size,
           font-weight,
           letter-spacing,
           line-height,
           text-indent,
           text-shadow,
           vertical-align,
           word-spacing,
           background,
           background-color,
           background-image,
           background-position,
           background-size,
           box-shadow,
           text-shadow,
           border,
           border-color,
           border-type,
           border-width,
           border-radius,
           height,
           width,
           padding,
           margin,
           top,
           right,
           bottom,
           left,
           z-index,
           opacity,
           perspective,
           perspective-origin,
           transform,
           transform-origin.

       (3) Text shadows:[offsetX || offsetY || blur || color]
            text-shadow: -4px -3px 1px rgba(45,153,38,0.64) ;

       (4) Box shadows:[offsetX || offsetY || blur || spread || type]
           -webkit-box-shadow: 4px 4px 3px 3px rgba(0,0,0,0.2) inset;
           box-shadow: 4px 4px 3px 3px rgba(0,0,0,0.2) inset;

